      <body>So my problems were rspec-releated: apparently rspec does not load controller behaviors unless the spec file is in spec/controllers. Moving all tests to spec/controllers allowed me to pull the include workaround out of my spec_helper. My specs were converted from testunit and had some outdated naming conventions, I guess.</body>
